Step 1)
- in Sections create "header.liquid" file 
1) first create all variables like 
 i.e 
 {%- liquid
  assign section_st = section.settings
  assign theme_st = settings
  assign section_width = section_st.section_width
  .
  .
 -%}

 2) we can add style also (optional)
    i.e. 
  {%- style -%}
    @media screen and (min-width: 768px) {
      header-inner.show-search-form.logo-left {
        grid-template-columns: auto auto 1fr;
      }
    }
  {%- endstyle -%}

3) add Schema code

4) add all html header code 
     <header>...</header>



Step 2)
- in Sections create "header-group.json" file 
- add code from main glozin file. 


Step 3) 
- Open "layout" folder and open "theme.liquid" file and check 
   {%- liquid
      sections 'header-group'
    -%}

     
